<i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>
<i>this is DJ Jack</i>

543
00:57:09,793 --> 00:57:11,528
<i>with an important update.</i>

544
00:57:11,662 --> 00:57:15,033
<i>Earlier this evening, the body</i>
<i>of a 17-year-old boy was found</i>

545
00:57:15,166 --> 00:57:16,700
